name: BONG BONK'S BROTHER
description: BONG, the younger sibling of BONK, harbors immense love for his brother. However, Bonk often feels embarrassed by Bong's constant indulgence in smoking. Undeterred, Bong is determined to match or even surpass Bonk's financial success. With a stroke of genius, he devises a brilliant plan to achieve his goal.
